document_data.name: Dynnatt
document_data.mainbody: '''Dynnatt''' was a small town located on the island of [[Gwynneth]] within the [[Moonshae Isles]].{{Cite interactive atlas}}{{Cite dungeon/196/Backdrop: The Moonshae Isles}}
document_data.Geography: Dynnatt was located in central [[Corwell]] in southern Gwynneth just southwest of [[Caer Corwell]]. The town was located among the moors in between the [[Corwell Road]] and [[Llyrath Forest]].
document_data.Inhabitants: The town was ruled by Lord [[Dynnatt]] in the {{YearlinkName|1345}}.{{Cite digital book/Darkwalker on Moonshae|1615}}
